name: SAKURA
description:
in a Japanese anime , Sakura or The cherry blossoms represented a symbol of friendship, goodwill, and political alliance between the two nations. Cherry blossoms are also used in anime to represent friendship and alliances
Cherry blossoms symbolize both birth and death, beauty and violence. They are a central motif in the Japanese worship of nature, but they have also historically signified the short but colorful life of the samurai.



2000*1400
